high_descs: Move around the island to the left and go to the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the dirty mug from in the cabinet above the microwave on the left.
Turn right, bring the mug to the sink, face the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Bring the washed mug to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Move to the microwave to the left around the counters.
Open the cabinet above the microwave, pick up the cup in the cabinet and close the door
Move to the sink to the right of you.
Place the cup in the sink and run some water before picking  it back up and turning the water off.
Move to the coffee pot to the left of you across from the microwave.
Place the cup on the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cup from the cabinet on the coffee pot.

high_descs: Go forward and then left and stand in front of the microwave.
Open the cabinet above and to the left and take out the mug.
Go right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the mug in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then take the mug out.
Go left and turn to face the coffee maker.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk until you clear the counter to your left then turn left and walk to the red microwave to the left of the stove in front of you.
Open the cabinet that's to the left of the microwave and get the dirty mug.
Turn right and walk to the sink on your left and then turn left to face it.
Clean the mug in the sink and then take it back out and shut off the tap.
Turn around and take two steps then turn right and walk over to the coffee maker.
Put the mug under the coffee makers spout.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and go left to stand in front of the microwave.
Open the cabinet on the left above the microwave and take out the cup.
Move to the right and face the sink.
Put the cup in the sink and then turn the water on and then off and then pick up the cup.
Turn around and cross to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Put the cup down under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cup under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Move to the microwave to the left of the sink
pick up a mug from the cabinet
move to the sink to the right
clean the mug in the sink
move to the coffee maker to the left of you
put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug on the coffee maker.
